    %% Platform orchestration
    RHODS -->|configures| DSC
    RHODS -->|configures| DSCI
    RHODS -->|deploys| Dashboard
    RHODS -->|deploys| NBController
    RHODS -->|deploys| KServe
    RHODS -->|deploys| ModelController
    RHODS -->|deploys| ModelMesh
    RHODS -->|deploys| DSPO
    RHODS -->|deploys| TrainingOp
    RHODS -->|deploys| KubeRay
    RHODS -->|deploys| CodeFlare
    RHODS -->|deploys| Kueue
    RHODS -->|deploys| TrustyAI

    %% Dashboard dependencies
    Dashboard -->|API calls| NBController
    Dashboard -->|API calls| KServe
    Dashboard -->|API calls| ModelMesh
    Dashboard -->|API calls| DSPO
    Dashboard -->|queries| Prometheus
    Dashboard -->|uses| OAuth
    Dashboard -->|uses| Routes

    %% Notebook Controller dependencies
    NBController -->|launches| Notebooks[Notebook Images]
    NBController -->|uses| OAuth
    NBController -->|uses| Routes
    NBController -->|uses| ServiceCA

    %% KServe dependencies (CRITICAL)
    KServe -->|requires| Knative
    KServe -->|requires| Istio
    KServe -->|uses| CertManager
    KServe -->|integrates| ModelController

    %% Model Controller dependencies
    ModelController -->|watches| KServe
    ModelController -->|creates| Routes
    ModelController -->|creates| Istio
    ModelController -->|integrates| Authorino[Authorino<br/>Auth Optional]

    %% ModelMesh dependencies
    ModelMesh -->|requires| etcd
    ModelMesh -->|loads from| S3

    %% Data Science Pipelines dependencies
    DSPO -->|deploys| Argo
    DSPO -->|deploys| Tekton
    DSPO -->|deploys| MariaDB
    DSPO -->|deploys| Minio
    DSPO -->|uses| S3

    %% Training Operator dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|optional| Volcano[Volcano<br/>Gang Scheduling]
    TrainingOp -->|optional| Kueue
    TrainingOp -->|uses| S3

    %% KubeRay dependencies
    KubeRay -->|manages| RayClusters[Ray Clusters]
    KubeRay -->|enhanced by| CodeFlare

    %% CodeFlare dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|watches| KubeRay
    CodeFlare -->|integrates| Kueue
    CodeFlare -->|uses| OAuth

    %% Kueue dependencies
    Kueue -->|queues| TrainingOp
    Kueue -->|queues| KubeRay
    Kueue -->|queues| DSPO

    %% TrustyAI dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| ModelMesh
    TrustyAI -->|exports to| Prometheus

    %% External service dependencies
    Notebooks -->|pulls from| Registry
    Notebooks -->|installs from| PyPI
    Notebooks -->|clones from| Git
    Notebooks -->|stores to| S3

    KServe -->|downloads from| S3
    KServe -->|pulls from| Registry

    ModelMesh -->|pulls from| Registry

    TrainingOp -->|pulls from| Registry
    DSPO -->|pulls from| Registry
    KubeRay -->|pulls from| Registry

    %% All operators to K8s API
    RHODS -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Dashboard -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    NBController -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    KServe -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    ModelController -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    ModelMesh -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    DSPO -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    TrainingOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    KubeRay -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    TrustyAI -->|API calls| K8sAPI

